    "You could instead decide to conform to the majority, opting for the far right (bandwagon effect).",
    "You could stay home and choose to abstain from voting-the cause is lost, anyway.",
    "In any case, this new probabilistic knowledge incentivises you to take a stance.",
    "What really differs from traditional polling is the granularity of the prediction.",
    "To put it bluntly, you feel an injunction either to oppose or to conform."
